00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:07.230
With so many villainous characters in fiction,
it's inevitable that some of their names,

00:00:07.230 --> 00:00:10.920
personalities, gimmicks and appearances will
be similar to others - there are only so many

00:00:10.920 --> 00:00:13.130
different ways to be evil, after all.

00:00:13.130 --> 00:00:17.430
That being said, you'll probably be surprised
at just how many creators ripped off other

00:00:17.430 --> 00:00:21.140
characters and real life people when it came
to conceiving some of these well-known bad

00:00:21.140 --> 00:00:22.140
guys.

00:00:22.140 --> 00:00:25.930
Some of the most iconic evil-doers ever to
appear in your favourite stories were actually

00:00:25.930 --> 00:00:30.400
blatantly stolen from other sources - both
real and fictional - and this video is going

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:32.349
to run you through just a few of them.

00:00:32.349 --> 00:00:35.760
Here are ten superhero villains who stole
people's identity.

